lead_paragraph: Penn State crossed several items off its to-do list Saturday in becoming bowl eligible, staying within a game of first place in the Big Ten East and ending a seven-game road losing streak.

headline.print_headline: Nittany Lions' Big Second Half Crushes Purdue, 62-24
